metadata.name: ‘ REMINISCE ‘ Vanilla
metadata.description:
'VANILLA' is part of my photographic art serie 
‘ REMINISCE ‘.

This  series is made in the COVID-period 2020.

The story behind it :
Reminiscing in a time of self isolation, looking back at some old photos, thinking about simple childhood food memories that made my happy as a little child, an often nostalgic recalling from long past and gone, that brings an image from the past into the mind, combining it into a few minimalistic conceptual images, together with some old kitchen tools that I have found in my grandmothers barn.

(The serie is six times Internationally awarded & shown on Belgian television)

In my work, i play with the viewers perception, exploring the boundaries of traditional photography combined with digital techniques.

1/1 edition ( 6910 x 4886 )

A physical print will be sent to the first collector

HandcraftedWithLoveBy_WesleyDombrecht
